308
00:21:34,711 --> 00:21:36,004
Es mi hijo, Michael.

309
00:21:36,004 --> 00:21:37,506
El Sr. Sabich.

310
00:21:37,506 --> 00:21:40,384
Hola, Michael.
Te acompaño en el sentimiento.

311
00:21:42,636 --> 00:21:43,679
Gracias.

312
00:21:51,979 --> 00:21:53,188
