413
00:28:50,230 --> 00:28:53,942
Te absorberá y te encerrarás en ti mismo.

414
00:29:03,368 --> 00:29:05,037
Y eso me matará.

415
00:29:58,715 --> 00:30:01,051
Mi padre engañó a mi madre.

416
00:30:05,556 --> 00:30:06,723
Y yo...

417
00:30:10,269 --> 00:30:13,397
